files.text: It appears, due to circumstances entirely out of my control, that despite every best effort I am forced to draw the conclusion from matters entirely separate from your actions that all fucks which were previously reserved here for your convenience have now found themselves within something of a deficit.

files.text: I’ve checked my _things to do_ list. I searched a lot but giving a fuck about you just isn’t there

files.text: Today’s lesson is titled _I don’t give a fuck about you_. Tomorrow’s lesson is the same as today’s!!

files.text: _Wanting_ you to fuck off and _giving_ a fuck about you are not the same thing. So fuck off!!
